{"tid":867045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支付寶正式與兩間專線小巴合作　　聲稱上車不會太慢靠銀彈幫忙？！","createTime":"2018-10-18T10:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T14:57:01.000Z","uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"04fcb3a7f8dea21e131bb6b3b142c34a4ca425e8","tid":867045,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/alipay-hk-minibus-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Falipay-hk-minibus-1.jpg&h=a43c139c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支付寶和微信支付在香港推行已有一段時間，雖然香港不少人都愛國愛黨都樂於使用，但無可否認其付費時速度會較慢。無論如何也好，支付寶香港今日宣佈與進智公共交通和冠榮車行合作，正式在小巴加裝新機，讓大家也可以用支付寶香港支付車資。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然其付費方式仍然是要靠QR Code，但支付寶稱他們加入了雙離線技術，就算訊號微弱或無訊號都可以用到，基本上可在0.3至0.4秒完成。另外，支付寶香港似乎還想用銀彈攻勢，無錢都上到車。因為他們表示若果就算忘記增值，它也可以讓用戶先乘車後付款，避免麻煩或影響速度。<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/10/zhifuzhengshixiaobahezuoshangbutaimankaomang/?fbclid=IwAR3ZfotqpwaulmZgpr-f4GYGy2RAoBxJl2CPuq7DQfv9TVUpPM6PG6sZGM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fzhifuzhengshixiaobahezuoshangbutaimankaomang%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ZfotqpwaulmZgpr-f4GYGy2RAoBxJl2CPuq7DQfv9TVUpPM6PG6sZGM4&d=48Q0sfUiPCFtPlwj4gyWouPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=6007b175\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/10/zhifuzhengshixiaobahezuoshangbutaimankaomang/?fbclid=IwAR3ZfotqpwaulmZgpr-f4GYGy2RAoBxJl2CPuq7DQfv9TVUpPM6PG6sZGM4</a>"},{"pid":"d20cccd0ecee418d98d77c10df2371312d536aec","tid":867045,"uid":215675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:30:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5236ac738fc52685910aa9550d04f08dc86d76f","tid":867045,"uid":19151,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"用八達通都可以塞撚住哂，更何況用app"},{"pid":"10f9a50cb999219069779905d3f4d860a6d8b8e1","tid":867045,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0